Format: JSON files for different types of data

URLs Accessed: List of URLs accessed by web_agent.js
Web Elements Interacted: CSS selectors, IDs, XPaths used in web_agent.js
Common Actions: Actions performed by web_agent.js, such as clicking, form submissions
Screenshots Captured: Details of screenshots captured by screenshot.js
Image Analysis: Patterns and data extracted from images by vision_scraper.py
Server Responses: Responses sent by server.js, including status codes and messages
Web Agent Decision Making: Decision-making processes in web_agent.js, influenced by GPT-4
Error Logs: Errors logged by server.js and web_agent.js
